	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S[alutem] d[ico].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Redeunt <placeName ref="l832">Galli</placeName> et <placeName ref="l862">Helvetii</placeName> ex <placeName ref="l834">Italia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Pacem fecit cum <persName>Philippo</persName> Gallus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Hunc audio per coronam suam jurasse, quod velit extirpare haeresim et in suo ipsius ordiri sanguine.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l569">Wormatia</placeName> discesserunt <persName ref="p6469">Schnepfius</persName>, <persName ref="p6369">Sarcerius</persName>, <persName ref="p3046">Victorinus</persName> et alii duo deserentes <persName ref="p2095">Melanchthonem</persName>, <persName ref="p458">Brentium</persName>, <persName>Pistorium</persName>, <placeName ref="l2477">Palatini</placeName> <placeName ref="l743">Pomeranique</placeName> principum theologos, qui noluerunt consentire in anathema et condemnationem nostrarum ecclesiarum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Datum, Unterschrift und Adresse wurden vom Abschreiber durch einen Vermerk am Briefanfang ersetzt:</hi> Idem eidem. <placeName ref="l587">Tiguro</placeName> Bernam. 24. octobris 1553.</note>]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
